drawnet.lib.filters
Class FilterDataOsMoSysIn

java.lang.Object
  drawnet.lib.filters.FilterData
      drawnet.lib.filters.FilterDataOsMoSysIn

public class FilterDataOsMoSysIn
extends FilterData

This class is an abstraction for an rsl OsMoSys file.
It may contain a set of frames.
Frames may contain elements or expressions.

See Also:
OsMoSysInFilter
